creator: CNCPTS
descriptionHtml:
Concepts opened their first doors in 1996, melding the worlds of street, skate and fashion years before it was commonplace. In the time since, Concepts has combined those authentic roots with their natural ability to convey a narrative and translate their identity through countless collaborative projects and original product.

24 years later, Concepts has spread their wings from Boston to New York, Dubai and China all while continuing to push boundaries through unmatched projects. Tracing a line from the inception of inspiration to the quality product, ending with a unique retail experience - Concepts tells a story through product like no other.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We are proud to announce the new CNCPTS app!
